dre se rindi\\u00f3, pero incluso tras la victoria, Fiora sab\\u00eda que la sombra de la duda siempre perseguir\\u00eda su reputaci\\u00f3n. En un intento de controlar su destino, Fiora prometi\\u00f3 superar el falso legado de su padre y demostrar que no solo es la mejor duelista de Demacia, sino de todo Valoran.<br \\/><br \\/>''''Vine aqu\\u00ed en busca de un desaf\\u00edo, \\u00bfesto es todo lo que estos necios pueden ofrecerme?''''<br \\/>-- Fiora<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"11","created":"2014-12-24 12:50:21","created_by":"911","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-12-24 19:39:57","modified_by":"911","checked_out":"911","checked_out_time":"2014-12-24 19:38:13","publish_up":"2014-12-24 12:50:21","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/LOLpersojanes\\\\\\/fiora.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/Joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/25\\",\\"urlatext\\":\\"Fiora Directora\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/Joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/24\\",\\"urlbtext\\":\\"Fiora Guardia Real\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/Joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/23\\",\\"urlctext\\":\\"Fiora Cuervo de la Noche\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\