derlands.wikia.com\\/wiki\\/Zer0?action=edit&amp;section=1\\">Editar secci\\u00f3n<\\/a><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>La capacidad activa de Zer0 crea una imagen residual por unos segundos, permitiendo distraer a los enemigos y atacarles por la espalda.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Mientras su habilidad est\\u00e1 activa, su da\\u00f1o cuerpo a cuerpo y armas aumenta de forma significativa, hasta que se agote el tiempo o ataque a un enemigo.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A medida que aumente de nivel, si nos centramos en mejorar su habilidad especial, podemos crear m\\u00e1s hologramas, que estos inflijan da\\u00f1o el\\u00e9ctrico al desaparecer, o potenciar el da\\u00f1o que infligimos para que sea m\\u00e1s letal.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"12","created":"2014-12-24 20:17:39","created_by":"911","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-12-25 00:25:09","modified_by":"911","checked_out":"911","checked_out_time":"2014-12-25 00:24:49","publish_up":"2014-12-24 20:17:39","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/borderlands2\\\\\\/asssasin-maddness-pack\\",\\"urlatext\\":\\"Pack Assessin Madness\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/borderlands2\\\\\\/asssasin-supreme-pack\\",\\"urlbtext\\":\\"Pack Assassin Supreme\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/borderlands2\\\\\\/assassin-cl0ckw0rk-pack\\",\\"urlctext\\":\\"Assassin Cl0ckw0rk Pack\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_positio