(135, 23, 1, '', '2015-01-16 19:23:01', 911, 2717, '3d3165742b2ee6b9e7f402c6ead57ca52e3d3d22', '{"id":23,"asset_id":"84","title":"Elise","alias":"elise","introtext":"<p>Personaje del Leage of Legends usados por la l\\u00ednea de arriba (TOP): Elise.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\"images\\/LOLpersojanes\\/elise.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>El carisma y la gracia de Elise ocultan el coraz\\u00f3n negro e inmisericorde de una depredadora letal. Due\\u00f1a de una implacable astucia, tienta a los incautos prometi\\u00e9ndoles el favor de la diosa ara\\u00f1a. Sacrific\\u00f3 su humanidad para transformarse en algo mucho m\\u00e1s siniestro y ahora sacrifica igualmente a los inocentes para preservar su poder y una juventud aparentemente eterna. Nadie sabe cu\\u00e1ntos han ca\\u00eddo en sus redes y han sido asesinados para saciar su insaciable apetito.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"11","created":"2014-12-24 12:36:12","created_by":"911","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-01-16 19:23:01","modified_by":"911","checked_out":"911","checked_out_time":"2015-01-16 19:22:50","publish_up":"2014-12-24 12:36:12","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/LOLpersojanes\\\\\\/elise.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/Joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/40\\",\\"urlatext\\":\\"Elise Sangrienta\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/Joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/39\\",\\"urlbtext\\":\\"Elise P\\\\u00e9talo de Muerte\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/Joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/38