_Sangre\\" class=\\"mw-headline\\">Sed De Sangre<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Esta habilidad al asesinar te dar\\u00e1 acumulaciones de Sed De Sangre las cuales te proporcionaran bonificaciones tales como, Aumento de da\\u00f1o, Aumento de velocidad y duracion de habilidad.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4><span id=\\"Mania\\" class=\\"mw-headline\\">Mania<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\"mw-headline\\">esta habilidad te dara bonificaciones cuerpo a cuerpo y de habilidad espectaculares como lanzar dinamita y detonrse a si mismo con ella para causar resultados explosivos.<\\/span><\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"15","created":"2014-12-24 20:34:45","created_by":"911","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-01-16 19:46:06","modified_by":"911","checked_out":"911","checked_out_time":"2015-01-16 19:45:57","publish_up":"2014-12-24 20:34:45","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/borderlands2\\\\\\/pshyco-supreme-pack\\",\\"urlatext\\":\\"Pack Psic\\\\u00f3pata supreme\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/borderlands2\\\\\\/pshyco-domination-pack\\",\\"urlbtext\\":\\"Pack Psic\\\\u00f3pata Domination\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/borderlands2\\\\\\/psycho-party-pack\\",\\"urlctext\\":\\"Psycho Party Pack\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent