(191, 41, 1, '', '2015-01-16 23:39:54', 911, 2599, '1f6f21cdc560d41384dc90b04866182745d5672d', '{"id":41,"asset_id":"114","title":"Thresh","alias":"thresh","introtext":"<p><img src=\\"images\\/LOLpersojanes\\/Thresh.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/>Thresh es un s\\u00e1dico segador espectral que disfruta atormentando a vivos y muertos por igual. En vida fue un carcelero que abusaba con brutalidad de los prisioneros, hasta el d\\u00eda en que estos lo colgaron de sus propias cadenas. Pero la mal\\u00e9fica esencia del Carcelero Implacable, liberada entonces, comenz\\u00f3 a vagar por Runaterra en busca de presas. Thresh disfruta de manera perversa quebrando poco a poco las mentes de quienes osan desafiarlo, antes de atrapar sus almas en la horripilante luz verde de su fanal.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"19","created":"2015-01-16 22:50:10","created_by":"911","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-01-16 23:39:54","modified_by":"911","checked_out":"911","checked_out_time":"2015-01-16 23:39:34","publish_up":"2015-01-16 22:50:10","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/60\\",\\"urlatext\\":\\"Thresh Campeonato\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/61\\",\\"urlbtext\\":\\"Thresh Luna de Sangre\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/localhost\\\\\\/joomla336\\\\\\/index.php\\\\\\/shopping\\\\\\/product\\\\\\/view\\\\\\/1\\\\\\/62\\",\\"urlctext\\":\\"Thresh Terror Nocturno\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_